{"tid":1561800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【埋大巴絲打同我入黎】理大罷課中期檢討問卷調查：同學之回應結果","createTime":"2019-09-11T17:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T00:39:45.000Z","uid":220045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6282a76d65cf93b91e251c46d6fc1cf9a04d39","tid":1561800,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"各位埋大巴絲打，理大罷委已經就住罷課中期檢討問卷調查整理左同學既回應，請大家參詳下同幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該哂<br />\n但因為Facebook page同連登都唔比我地upload PDF，所以如果大家想攞份文件既原件，就要入我地個Channel度攞。罷委TG channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/polyudongotoschool\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpolyudongotoschool&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=45575273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/polyudongotoschool</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致各位香港理工大學同學：<br />\n<br />\n【理大罷課中期檢討問卷調查：同學之回應結果】<br />\n<br />\n由大專學界發動的罷課行動已經進行了多於一星期，香港理工大學罷課委員會（理大罷委）在大專學界提出的政府回應限期前進行了中期檢討問卷調查，並於9月8日在網上不同平台邀請了理大同學填寫問卷，期望就著罷課得到更多意見。問卷已於9月10日午夜截止，並收到了149個有效回覆。罷委就著同學的回應做了一份報告，內容可參閱隨此文上載的PDF文件。<br />\n<br />\n從此份問卷調查的回應中看出，就著罷課以及整場社會運動，不少理大同學也十分關注。理大罷委想藉此機會感謝一眾回應了問卷調查的同學，以及在罷課區、TG group、Facebook等不同渠道曾向罷委給予意見的同學。罷委會認真看待同學的意見，希望能在這運動中出一分綿力。同時，罷委留意到有不少同學都對理大中其他持分者有些意見，而同學提出的相應建議也很有用處，相信是重要的提醒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，9月13日是學界對林鄭政府回應市民訴求的死線，罷委期望學界於當天有相應行動，同時鼓勵學校中不同持份者均會盡力參與。<br />\n<br />\n理大罷委衷心希望各位同學能在這風雨飄搖的時刻能謹守岡位，莫忘初心。正義或會遲來，但我們必定能等到。罷委再次謝謝各位同學在罷課期間付出的努力！<br />\n<br />\n香港理工大學罷課委員會上<br />\n二零一九年九月十二日<br />\n<br />\nFacebook post link：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/115210413184418/posts/123046745734118/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F115210413184418%2Fposts%2F123046745734118%2F&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=630d50ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/115210413184418/posts/123046745734118/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求幫推！！！！！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"700fe788d7514a1b8344a511febd67b494383128","tid":1561800,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d73bee8f25120194679d9804c39d54797d164a2","tid":1561800,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:37:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0e301d223f5b11f0078c8162bbaea123575c2302","tid":1561800,"uid":106478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"915<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三百萬人 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fd161a324f02b2cab3cf1c09daa89a5ca103db","tid":1561800,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:41:21.000Z","msg":"自推，希望埋大仔女都睇到"},{"pid":"199bc47c4e30b97f33fad631170f405a8cce1779","tid":1561800,"uid":106938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06366a3dfa3e48e54dfae45f2ecbbe8992fbfed","tid":1561800,